  "text": "The authoritative source for go.etcd.io/etcd/client/v3 is the etcd-io/etcd repository. The module declaration `module go.etcd.io/etcd/client/v3` is at client/v3/go.mod in the etcd-io/etcd repository. Evidence: The file client/v3/go.mod in github.com/sg-evals/etcd-io-etcd (the Sourcegraph mirror of etcd-io/etcd) contains the module declaration on line 1: 'module go.etcd.io/etcd/client/v3'. This is the authoritative declaration. Other repositories such as kubernetes/kubernetes and grafana/grafana depend on this module but do not declare it, confirming that etcd-io/etcd is the source of truth."
}

